an>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setGroupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>GroupFilter<span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>initGroupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 필터 속성을 변경하는 함수를 구현해 보자.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-onchange-함수-구현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-onchange-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"2 onchange 함수 구현 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(2) onChange 함수 구현</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"51554590427533970000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`  const onChangePeriod = (period: number[]) => {\r\n    setGroupFilter({\r\n      ...groupFilter,\r\n      period: {\r\n        ...groupFilter.period,\r\n        min: period[0],\r\n        max: period[1],\r\n      },\r\n    });\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  const onChangeLinkMode = (isLinkMode: boolean) => {\r\n    setGroupFilter({\r\n      ...groupFilter,\r\n      period: {\r\n        ...groupFilter.period,\r\n        isLinkMode,\r\n      },\r\n    });\r\n  };`, `51554590427533970000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\">  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onChangePeriod</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>period<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token function\">setGroupFilter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      period<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>period<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        min<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> period<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        max<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> period<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onChangeLinkMode</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>isLinkMode<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token function\">setGroupFilter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      period<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>period<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        isLinkMode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>앞으로 추가해야할 속성이 많이 남았는데 필터링하는 각 탭에서 각자 이렇게 함수를 구현하면 디버깅이 힘들어질 것 같다. 또한 로직도 길어져서 컴포넌트에서 분리가 필요해 보인다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-usereducer로-객체-관리하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-usereducer%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 usereducer로 객체 관리하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. useReducer로 객체 관리하기</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">useReducer</code>를 사용하면 상태 업데이트하는 컴포넌트와 로직 분리가 용이하며 <code class=\"language-text\">reducer</code>라는 함수에서 모든 로직을 관리할 수 있으므로 디버깅이 편해진다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-reducer-선언\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-reducer-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8\" aria-label=\"1 reducer 선언 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(1) reducer 선언</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"3676590455329309000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`  const initGroupFilter: GroupFilter = {\r\n    period: {\r\n      min: MIN_PERIOD,\r\n      max: MAX_PERIOD,\r\n      isLinkMode: false,\r\n    },\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  const reducer = (groupFilter: GroupFilter, action: Action): GroupFilter => {\r\n    switch (action.type) {\r\n      case &quot;PERIOD&quot;:\r\n        return { ...groupFilter, period: action.payload };\r\n      default:\r\n        throw new Error(&quot;Unhandled group filter action&quot;);\r\n    }\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  const [groupFilter, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, initGroupFilter);`, `3676590455329309000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\">  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> initGroupFilter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> GroupFilter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    period<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      min<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">MIN_PERIOD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      max<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">MAX_PERIOD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      isLinkMode<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> reducer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> GroupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> action<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Action<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> GroupFilter <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">switch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>action<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"PERIOD\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> period<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> action<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>payload <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Unhandled group filter action\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>groupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dispatch<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useReducer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>reducer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> initGroupFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 한 파일에서 상태 업데이트 로직을 모두 관리할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-dispatch-사용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-dispatch-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"2 dispatch 사용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(2) dispatch 사용</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"54444968791158170000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`dispatch({ type: &quot;PERIOD&quot;, payload });`, `54444968791158170000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token function\">dispatch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> type<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"PERIOD\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> payload <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컴포넌트에서는 이렇게 간단하게 호출만하여 상태를 업데이트 할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-custom-hook으로-분리하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-custom-hook%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B6%84%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"4 custom hook으로 분리하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. custom hook으로 분리하기</h2>\n<p>이제와서 다시 정리해보니 굳이 <code class=\"language-text\">useReducer</code>를 사용하지 않아도 되었다.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">useState</code>를 사용하고 <code class=\"language-text\">custom hook</code>으로 분리만 하면 로직 분리도 가능하고 상태 업데이트 로직도 한곳에 모을 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-마치며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"5 마치며 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 마치며</h2>\n<p>결국 중요한 것은 <code class=\"language-text\">view</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">logic</code>의 분리라고 생각한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">view</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">logic</code>의 분리하면</p>\n<ol>\n<li>테스트가 용이해진다.</li>\n<li>디버깅이 용이해진다.</li>\n<li>코드 가독성이 좋아진다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">useReducer</code>로 구현하든 <code class=\"language-text\">custom hook</code>으로 구현하든 목적은 <code class=\"language-text\">logic</code>은 <code class=\"language-text\">hook</code>으로 구현, 컴포넌트 내에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">view</code>만 구현하는 것이며, 컴포넌트 내에서는 추상화된 <code class=\"language-text\">logic</code>을 간단하게 호출하여 사용하는 것이다.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#0-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\">0. 들어가며</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%9A%94%EA%B5%AC%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\">1. 프로젝트 요구사항</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-usestate%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">2. useState로 객체 관리하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-usestate-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8\">(1) useState 선언</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-onchange-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\">(2) onChange 함수 구현</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-usereducer%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">3. useReducer로 객체 관리하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-reducer-%EC%84%A0%